    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable dings, some paint fading on the hood, and minor rust spots around the wheel wells. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear, and the air conditioning takes a few minutes to reach full cooling capacity. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but the suspension is starting to feel loose and it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable, functional vehicle who doesn't mind putting in a little work to bring it back to its best.",
