    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive masterpiece in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved, featuring a mirror-finish exterior completely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections, further enhanced by a multi-stage ceramic coating. The interior is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery remains taut with no bolster wear, and the high-gloss trim pieces are devoid of scratches. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians, with all service records organized in a comprehensive portfolio. Always stored in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in rain, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. It is, quite simply, the finest example currently available on the market.",
